description.en: Truckers.FM is the No.1 Hit Music Station as voted by the TruckersMP Community 5 years, providing round the clock entertainment broadcasting a variety of shows, ranging from the Top 40 to the biggest throwbacks.
description.ga_IE: Is é Truckers.fm an stáisiún ceoil Uimh.1 buailte mar a vótáil an pobal TruckersMP 5 bliana, ag soláthar siamsaíochta an chloig ag craoladh seónna éagsúla, ag dul ó na 40 barr go dtí na caithimh is mó.
